channel.title: Looking for coders for the ''Tocex'' project. Server is up and running
channel.description:
Dear Moparscape members, first things first, I would like to apologize to Moparscape's staff, if I've posted in the wrong area, SORRY!
OT: I've quit coding server's about 3-4 years ago, I've seen how big RSPS communities are getting, and RSPS<RS, Anyway, am looking for a dedicated team, who are willing to help me with the Tocex project, I need java coders, HTML and MySQL coders, as personally I don't understand HTML and MySQL language, once the project is complete, I will host it my self on a powerful Dedicated Server.
What will you get in return? As we start growing bigger we will have more players, any profit made, will be split between the team and ofc you will be known as a dedicated developer etc.
BEFORE you start flaming, I am serious about this, and hopefully I will find my team and make the project as big as Near Reality is to this day.
Thank You for taking your time and reading this.
Here is the form if you are interested.
Current possitions
Owner/Coder; David/Myself Dedicated Coder: OPEN Webmaster: Soul My Maul MySQL Coder: OPEN GFX Artist: OPEN
Position: MSN/EMAIL: Years in RSPS/Java: Why you want to join: Some previous work: UPDATE: this what I've done so far; [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/a5g6q1.png[/img] [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/10pr0ad.png[/img] [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/2uh7i4p.png[/img] [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/jfckzq.png[/img] [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/2zz4uo8.png[/img]
You May Now Carry On Flaming....
